Running multiple retail locations in 2026 means choosing an ecommerce platform that won't buckle under operational complexity. Our team has evaluated both Shopify and BigCommerce across operators managing anywhere from 3 boutiques to 50+ franchise locations. The differences that matter aren't in marketing materials—they're in what breaks at 2 AM during a holiday rush.

This comparison cuts through the noise. We'll cover real pricing at scale, inventory sync reliability, multi-currency handling, and the hidden costs that surface once you're locked in.

